  <h2>What is ANKA?</h2>
  <div class="callout green">
    <div class="callout-title">Core Positioning Statement</div>
    <p>ANKA is an AI-native revenue cycle execution platform built for mid-market healthcare. We close the gap between what healthcare organizations should be collecting and what they actually collect — by turning remittance data, payer contracts, and claim intelligence into automated revenue recovery.<br><br><strong>Tagline: "AI that executes your AR"</strong></p>
  </div>
  <p>ANKA operates as a backend execution layer on top of existing RCM workflows. It does not replace billing teams, EHRs, or PMS systems. It does what those systems cannot: execute the work that would otherwise go unworked.</p>

