<section id="s03">
  <div class="section-label">03 — The Problem We Solve</div>
  <h2>The Execution Problem</h2>
  <div class="callout amber">
    <div class="callout-title">The Core Insight — Memorise This</div>
    <p>The revenue cycle problem for mid-market healthcare is NOT a data problem, an insight problem, or a technology problem. It is an <strong>EXECUTION problem</strong>. The work that needs to happen — appealing denials, following up with payers, identifying underpayments, working aged AR — simply doesn't get done.</p>
  </div>

  <h3>Three Execution Failures</h3>
